  "texts": [
    "We once more focus only on the data condition where the ruby is revealed.",
    "The results of this exercise are presented in plots ii) of Panel A and Panel B in Figure 6.",
    "Like before, we see that exploration monotonically increases with the number of pro-social agents, as does the share of agents that find the diamond.",
    "Once again, the rationales are instructive.",
    "As one pro-social agent tells us, \"Since I am pro-social and aim to give other participants the chance to discover a diamond, I will choose a mountain that has not been selected by others yet."
  ],
